Class IzouExtensionFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ro.fortsoft.pf4j.DefaultExtensionFinder
      • intellimate.izou.addon.IzouExtensionFinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, ro.fortsoft.pf4j.ExtensionFinder, ro.fortsoft.pf4j.PluginStateListener

    public class IzouExtensionFinder
extends ro.fortsoft.pf4j.DefaultExtensionFinder
    The default implementation for ExtensionFinder. All extensions declared in a plugin are indexed in a file "META-INF/extensions.idx". This class lookup extensions in all extensions index files "META-INF/extensions.idx".
